";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Tue, 27 Feb 2018 16:31:48 +0000";s:4:"guid";s:27:"388 at http://bcfmradio.com";s:8:"comments";s:72:"http://bcfmradio.com/events/diversity-awards-announced-19th-may#comments";s:7:"summary";s:4257:"<div class="galleryformatter galleryview galleryformatter-greenarrows">
