          <a href="http://bcfmradio.com/sites/default/files/field/photostream/PaulS%20diversity%20award.jpg" title="BCfm10 Birthday Celebrations and Bristol Diversity Awards image 1" class="shownext"><span class="view-full" title="View the full image">View the full image</span></a><img src="http://bcfmradio.com/sites/default/files/styles/galleryformatter_slide/public/field/photostream/PaulS%20diversity%20award.jpg?itok=7igAG4NT" width="570" height="230" alt="" title="BCfm10 Birthday Celebrations and Bristol Diversity Awards image 1" />                  </li>
